thread.title: Lottie Anderson

author: Lottie Anderson
title: Lottie Anderson
text: I purchased 63XL bulk ink. When price comparing with Big W, I saved $33.20. The order was delivered within 4 business days, which is incredibly good as I live in rural Australia and it's rare for orders to arrive so quickly. Communication was of high quality, notifying me of confirmation, dispatch, and delivery. Highly reccomend printzone for both price and quality service.
